==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adorer
<hw>A*dor"er</hw> <pr>(⟦adot⟧*d⟦omac⟧r"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>One who adores; a worshiper; one who admires or loves greatly; an
ardent admirer.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧An <xex>adorer</xex> of truth.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Clarendon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I profess myself her <qex>adorer</qex>, not her friend.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>adoring</ent>⟦br⟧
